					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p4611"></a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=4611&amp;sid=921628ea43ee614e5aa5959379af07a0#p4611"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri Sep 16, 2005 5:07 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
